about.text:
I am a Web Developer in constant training, I am passionate about learning new techniques and languages. I'm currently working as a Back-End Developer in Bilbomatica and in my free time I'm training in Angular in a self-taught way with courses and personal projects.
 
I am Open to face new work challenges do not hesitate to contact!
    
    Skills:
    - HTML
    - CSS, SASS, Bootstrap
    - JavaScript, TypeScript
    - Training in Angular
    - SQL and NoSQL databases
    - Git - GitHub
    - JAVA, Object Oriented Programming
   
I also have knowledge in Linux, Docker, Firebase and AWS (basic level).
